    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted despite one factor (Test conditions) achieving level 2 against a required level of 3. All three primary QoIs meet quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96; QoI difference < 10%). The single-condition testing gap is acknowledged but does not preclude acceptance given the strong output comparison results and high relevance of the validation activities to the COU. The credibility claim for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw FEA framework is considered adequately supported for the stated intended use.",
